1
00:00:04,050 --> 00:00:06,999
♫ <i> Nowhere to escape </i> ♫

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:09,959
♫ <i> No one to rely on </i> ♫

3
00:00:09,960 --> 00:00:14,120
♫ <i> Withdrawing smiles </i> ♫

4
00:00:15,960 --> 00:00:18,869
♫ <i> Never give in </i> ♫

5
00:00:18,870 --> 00:00:24,140
♫ <i> Forget about one's youth </i> ♫

6
00:00:25,950 --> 00:00:28,819
♫ <i> I've never been afraid of loneliness when
embarking on this journey </i> ♫

7
00:00:28,819 --> 00:00:31,789
♫ <i> Tears and regrets go hand in hand </i> ♫

8
00:00:31,790 --> 00:00:34,789
♫ <i> But my heart is still fiery-hot </i> ♫

9
00:00:34,790 --> 00:00:37,739
♫ <i>To the distance</i> ♫

10
00:00:37,739 --> 00:00:40,809
♫ <i>The miserable past is like a dagger</i> ♫

11
00:00:40,809 --> 00:00:43,619
♫ <i>Though my wings are broken</i> ♫

12
00:00:43,619 --> 00:00:49,930
♫ <i>I will keep flying</i> ♫

13
00:00:52,520 --> 00:00:56,199
♫ <i>Following the direction of the light</i> ♫

14
00:00:56,200 --> 00:00:58,359
♫ <i>I'll forget you</i> ♫

15
00:00:58,360 --> 00:01:04,170
♫ <i>The memory shaped my stubbornness</i> ♫

16
00:01:04,170 --> 00:01:07,359
♫ <i>By virtue of the light in the dark night</i> ♫

17
00:01:07,360 --> 00:01:10,309
♫ <i>I'll return it with a long ballad</i> ♫

18
00:01:10,310 --> 00:01:12,269
♫ <i>The river of life is under my feet</i> ♫

19
00:01:12,270 --> 00:01:16,950
♫ <i>I don't regret my craziness</i> ♫

20
00:01:25,855 --> 00:01:32,654
<i>[The Long Ballad]</i>

21
00:01:32,654 --> 00:01:36,240
<i>[Episode 02]</i>

22
00:01:39,319 --> 00:01:41,350
Greetings, Father.

23
00:01:41,350 --> 00:01:44,950
That "lad" who reversed the game today. It was you, right?

24
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:48,309
I didn't mean to break into the arena.

25
00:01:48,310 --> 00:01:50,821
But we were on a losing streak at that time.

26
00:01:50,822 --> 00:01:52,790
So...

27
00:01:54,233 --> 00:01:56,660
that's why I had to...

28
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:03,640
Well done.

29
00:02:04,633 --> 00:02:06,654
You've brought not only the treasured dagger,

30
00:02:06,654 --> 00:02:08,787
but also honor for me.

31
00:02:08,787 --> 00:02:11,754
Your Grandfather heard it and requested my presence at once.

32
00:02:11,754 --> 00:02:13,176
He praised you very highly

33
00:02:13,176 --> 00:02:15,250
and gave many rewards.

34
00:02:15,250 --> 00:02:18,320
I've never thought that a girl

35
00:02:18,320 --> 00:02:23,150
could do better than your brothers.

36
00:02:23,150 --> 00:02:25,365
Thanks for the praise, Father.

37
00:02:25,365 --> 00:02:30,570
Changge, where's the Ashile Tribe's treasured sword?

38
00:02:30,570 --> 00:02:31,943
Send it to my room.

39
00:02:31,943 --> 00:02:34,200
I want to appreciate it.

40
00:02:34,900 --> 00:02:38,770
I've already sent it to Second Uncle.

41
00:02:40,044 --> 00:02:41,770
What?

42
00:02:42,877 --> 00:02:45,710
How "good and dutiful" you are!

43
00:02:45,710 --> 00:02:47,810
It's me who's raised you

44
00:02:47,810 --> 00:02:51,359
but how can you send the treasure to other people?

45
00:02:51,359 --> 00:02:53,870
Second Uncle is also my family...

46
00:02:53,870 --> 00:02:56,279
He's your family, so what about me?

47
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:58,176
How dare you take his side?

48
00:02:58,176 --> 00:03:01,232
Changge, from now on,

49
00:03:01,232 --> 00:03:06,243
I want you to mention nothing about the Qin Family.

50
00:03:06,244 --> 00:03:08,440
Father, you've misunderstood me.

51
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:10,540
- I...
- Your Highness, please calm down.

52
00:03:12,839 --> 00:03:14,921
Your Highness, please calm down.

53
00:03:14,921 --> 00:03:16,465
Mr. Wei.

54
00:03:16,465 --> 00:03:18,210
Advisor Wei.
<i>[Wei Zheng]</i>

55
00:03:18,210 --> 00:03:20,543
You finally come to see me.

56
00:03:20,543 --> 00:03:23,543
Your Highness, she's still young

57
00:03:23,543 --> 00:03:26,887
so you need not flare up for it.

58
00:03:26,888 --> 00:03:28,620
She's unfilial!

59
00:03:28,620 --> 00:03:30,469
She only cares about Prince Qin!

60
00:03:30,470 --> 00:03:33,879
I don't think she is concerned for me!

61
00:03:33,879 --> 00:03:34,921
Your Highness.

62
00:03:34,921 --> 00:03:36,376
Wei Zheng!

63
00:03:36,377 --> 00:03:37,665
Don't waste time!

64
00:03:37,666 --> 00:03:39,660
Come with me!

65
00:03:39,660 --> 00:03:41,200
Yes.

66
00:03:41,900 --> 00:03:43,500
Leave here.

67
00:03:44,711 --> 00:03:47,443
Go to Prince Qi's Manor and ask Yuanji to come here at once!

68
00:03:47,444 --> 00:03:49,070
Yes.

69
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:57,560
<i>[Everlasting Celebration of Virtue House]</i>

70
00:04:05,566 --> 00:04:07,560
- Mother.
- Halt there!

71
00:04:11,977 --> 00:04:16,550
You don't take my advice anymore, right?

72
00:04:16,550 --> 00:04:19,430
Then, what did I tell you yesterday?

73
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:21,499
I just...

74
00:04:21,499 --> 00:04:24,199
You just went over the wall and dressed up as a player

75
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:28,010
to be in the limelight in front of the Ashile, right?

76
00:04:28,010 --> 00:04:31,177
Mother... I won the game.

77
00:04:31,177 --> 00:04:34,760
Father said that Grandfather praised me a lot.

78
00:04:51,959 --> 00:04:54,450
You've never slapped me before...

79
00:04:55,279 --> 00:04:57,590
You've been wild since your childhood,

80
00:04:57,590 --> 00:05:00,079
always making trouble.

81
00:05:00,079 --> 00:05:02,159
I'm to blame for not lecturing you well.

82
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:04,719
You've been spoiled by me.

83
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:07,643
How dare you fight for the limelight against men?

84
00:05:07,644 --> 00:05:09,720
Why mention it?

85
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:11,700
Men and women should be equal.

86
00:05:11,700 --> 00:05:13,319
Why do you always think

87
00:05:13,320 --> 00:05:15,750
I'm not as good as a man?

88
00:05:15,750 --> 00:05:18,179
I'm able-bodied. I have skills.

89
00:05:18,179 --> 00:05:19,739
I can go wherever I want!

90
00:05:19,739 --> 00:05:21,790
You can go nowhere!

91
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:23,520
Mother.

92
00:05:25,888 --> 00:05:27,610
Follow me.

93
00:05:32,211 --> 00:05:33,940
Kneel down.

94
00:05:34,711 --> 00:05:36,310
Mother.

95
00:05:36,310 --> 00:05:37,970
Kneel!

96
00:05:42,911 --> 00:05:45,620
Take an oath here.

97
00:05:46,322 --> 00:05:48,300
From now on,

98
00:05:48,300 --> 00:05:50,000
no matter what happens

99
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:52,200
and what you go through,

100
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:56,365
you must live with no hate forever.

101
00:05:56,365 --> 00:05:59,210
Mother... I've never hated anyone.

102
00:05:59,210 --> 00:06:01,510
I need your pledge.

103
00:06:03,299 --> 00:06:06,260
Okay. I swear.

104
00:06:06,260 --> 00:06:08,421
But if someone harms you,

105
00:06:08,421 --> 00:06:10,490
I shall certainly hate the guy.

106
00:06:19,744 --> 00:06:22,290
No one will harm me.

107
00:06:22,290 --> 00:06:25,630
I only hope...

108
00:06:25,630 --> 00:06:29,550
that you can be happy and unfettered forever.

109
00:06:30,299 --> 00:06:35,230
Stay away from disputes and mishaps.

110
00:06:35,230 --> 00:06:38,010
As long as my mother stays with me,

111
00:06:38,010 --> 00:06:40,370
I'm the happiest girl in the world.

112
00:06:42,559 --> 00:06:47,060
Do not forget what you've sworn here.

113
00:06:47,060 --> 00:06:49,932
Okay. I'll keep it in mind.

114
00:06:49,932 --> 00:06:51,670
Fine.

115
00:06:51,670 --> 00:06:53,321
Go back and pack.

116
00:06:53,321 --> 00:06:55,860
You'll be sent to Biyong Hall tomorrow.

117
00:06:55,860 --> 00:06:58,000
Read and repent there for ten days.

118
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,921
You must never escape again.

119
00:06:59,921 --> 00:07:01,660
Mother.

120
00:07:01,660 --> 00:07:03,410
It's my decision.

121
00:07:03,410 --> 00:07:05,560
Nobody can change it.

122
00:07:08,444 --> 00:07:10,110
Mother...

123
00:07:16,055 --> 00:07:17,076
Report to General.

124
00:07:17,076 --> 00:07:19,754
Li Jiancheng and Li Shimin balance in power but are discordant.

125
00:07:19,755 --> 00:07:22,420
We don't know who will be the heir.

126
00:07:22,420 --> 00:07:24,332
Li Yuanji will soon lead troops to Wu City.

127
00:07:24,332 --> 00:07:28,330
We know nothing about his power and plan.

128
00:07:28,330 --> 00:07:30,399
What has he done recently?

129
00:07:30,399 --> 00:07:33,380
Nothing special. He's been visiting Li Jiancheng every night.

130
00:07:33,399 --> 00:07:35,799
It's said they're close.

131
00:07:35,799 --> 00:07:38,140
He did nothing unusual.

132
00:07:38,140 --> 00:07:40,860
Nothing unusual?

133
00:07:42,022 --> 00:07:45,600
Conceal your whereabouts and spy on them.

134
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:49,010
Report to me about all the details,

135
00:07:49,010 --> 00:07:53,590
including the things not unusual.

136
00:07:53,590 --> 00:07:55,000
Yes.

137
00:08:06,711 --> 00:08:09,830
<i>[Li Chunfeng]</i>

138
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:17,160
<i>Abnormal astrology.</i>

139
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:19,630
<i>A new monarch.</i>

140
00:08:19,630 --> 00:08:21,650
<i>The world will be changed.</i>

141
00:08:21,650 --> 00:08:23,170
<i>[Obey the heavens for answers to the people]</i>

142
00:08:23,170 --> 00:08:24,950
Get the cart.

143
00:08:24,950 --> 00:08:26,487
I want to go to the palace.

144
00:08:26,488 --> 00:08:28,160
Yes.

145
00:08:29,722 --> 00:08:33,950
<i>[East Palace]</i>

146
00:08:47,511 --> 00:08:49,100
Princess!

147
00:08:53,622 --> 00:08:57,149
Princess, Madam made you some pastries.

148
00:08:57,149 --> 00:08:59,321
All your favorites.

149
00:08:59,321 --> 00:09:04,330
And also, she made you some clothes.

150
00:09:04,330 --> 00:09:07,200
I'm out for a few days and I'll be back soon.

151
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:09,110
Why did she...

152
00:09:09,110 --> 00:09:12,038
She stayed up all night.

153
00:09:12,039 --> 00:09:14,276
She's worried about you.

154
00:09:14,276 --> 00:09:17,770
But why doesn't she come to see me off?

155
00:09:17,770 --> 00:09:21,110
She's... tired.

156
00:09:22,388 --> 00:09:24,865
Nanny San, by the way, Yueyan doesn't know that I'm leaving.

157
00:09:24,866 --> 00:09:27,740
Don't forget to tell her to wait for me to return.

158
00:09:27,740 --> 00:09:29,132
You can be at ease.

159
00:09:29,132 --> 00:09:31,143
You've been friends since childhood,

160
00:09:31,143 --> 00:09:33,490
so she won't get angry with you.

161
00:09:39,900 --> 00:09:42,432
Well... Nanny San, it's time for me to leave.

162
00:09:42,432 --> 00:09:45,010
Take care of yourself and my mother.

163
00:09:45,010 --> 00:09:46,770
Wait for me.

164
00:09:48,777 --> 00:09:50,310
Here you are.

165
00:09:51,677 --> 00:09:53,460
Take it.

166
00:09:55,255 --> 00:09:56,990
Mother!

167
00:09:59,290 --> 00:10:02,670
<i>[East Palace]</i>

168
00:10:02,670 --> 00:10:04,911
Mother, you ask me to leave

169
00:10:04,911 --> 00:10:07,040
but also hate to part with me.

170
00:10:12,433 --> 00:10:14,040
Changge,

171
00:10:14,040 --> 00:10:16,238
Biyong Hall is different from here.

172
00:10:16,239 --> 00:10:18,920
The servants there are not that meticulous,

173
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:21,670
so can you take special care of yourself?

174
00:10:21,688 --> 00:10:23,521
When meals don't agree well with you,

175
00:10:23,521 --> 00:10:27,520
can you make yourself a few delicious dishes?

176
00:10:28,459 --> 00:10:30,800
As your clothes are torn

177
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:33,210
and I'm not at your side,

178
00:10:33,210 --> 00:10:37,330
sew it yourself according to how Nanny San taught you.

179
00:10:38,088 --> 00:10:40,630
Put on more clothes,

180
00:10:40,630 --> 00:10:43,160
if it's rainy or snowy.

181
00:10:44,155 --> 00:10:46,410
Mother.

182
00:10:46,410 --> 00:10:48,054
How about I not go

183
00:10:48,054 --> 00:10:50,630
and stay with you?

184
00:10:50,630 --> 00:10:52,240
Can I?

185
00:10:55,711 --> 00:10:57,054
No.

186
00:10:57,054 --> 00:10:58,940
Set out at once.

187
00:10:58,940 --> 00:11:01,587
Do not come back without my permission!

188
00:11:01,587 --> 00:11:03,430
Mother.

189
00:11:04,988 --> 00:11:06,870
Mother.

190
00:11:11,655 --> 00:11:13,440
Fine, I'm leaving.

191
00:11:22,811 --> 00:11:24,580
Changge.

192
00:11:25,577 --> 00:11:27,440
Could you...

193
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:30,140
call me "mother" once again?

194
00:12:02,255 --> 00:12:04,120
Madam.

195
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:08,250
You hate to part but why do you...

196
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:14,080
Only in this way can she live a good life.

197
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:06,450
<i>The mission will depart tomorrow.</i>

198
00:13:06,450 --> 00:13:09,310
<i>Shixin Sili, lead a group and ride north</i>

199
00:13:09,310 --> 00:13:11,459
<i>and report the situation to Khan.</i>

200
00:13:11,459 --> 00:13:14,930
<i>I'll stay here to continue exploring.</i>

201
00:13:34,811 --> 00:13:36,350
Scatter.

202
00:14:22,788 --> 00:14:26,220
<i>[Xuanwu Gate]</i>

203
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:44,800
Close the gate and lock it at once!

204
00:15:02,855 --> 00:15:04,350
<i>Hurry!</i>

205
00:15:08,288 --> 00:15:09,410
<i>Wait.</i>

206
00:15:09,410 --> 00:15:11,043
<i>We're not driving northward to leave.</i>

207
00:15:11,044 --> 00:15:13,410
<i>It's not the way to Biyong.</i>

208
00:15:14,644 --> 00:15:16,199
Is it the wrong way?

209
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:18,400
It's not the way to Biyong.

210
00:15:18,400 --> 00:15:19,909
We didn't go wrong.

211
00:15:19,909 --> 00:15:21,310
Princess, don't worry.

212
00:15:21,310 --> 00:15:25,950
Madam has told me to send you there safely.

213
00:15:25,950 --> 00:15:28,380
<i>She's been weird since yesterday.</i>

214
00:15:28,380 --> 00:15:30,843
<i>Where is she going to send me?</i>

215
00:15:30,843 --> 00:15:32,690
<i>Hurry!</i>

216
00:15:32,690 --> 00:15:34,110
Hold on.

217
00:15:34,110 --> 00:15:37,250
She's never treated me in this way before.

218
00:15:37,250 --> 00:15:39,560
She must be keeping something back from me.

219
00:16:09,666 --> 00:16:11,820
<i>[East Palace]</i>

220
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:22,670
<i>Blood?</i>

221
00:16:23,999 --> 00:16:25,890
<i>What's happened?</i>

222
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,810
<i>Where are they?</i>

223
00:16:58,840 --> 00:17:01,030
<i>Why is there so much blood here?</i>

224
00:17:02,211 --> 00:17:04,030
<i>Why?</i>

225
00:17:07,660 --> 00:17:09,510
<i>Why?</i>

226
00:17:10,130 --> 00:17:12,560
<i>Why is no one here?</i>

227
00:17:39,166 --> 00:17:41,030
<i>Mother.</i>

228
00:17:41,030 --> 00:17:43,210
<i>Please be safe!</i>

229
00:17:45,333 --> 00:17:47,220
Follow up!

230
00:17:47,220 --> 00:17:48,620
Hurry!

231
00:17:48,620 --> 00:17:50,470
Keep the pace!

232
00:17:52,344 --> 00:17:53,940
Go!

233
00:17:53,940 --> 00:17:55,332
Hurry up!

234
00:17:55,332 --> 00:17:57,030
Be quick!

235
00:17:59,111 --> 00:18:01,160
<i>How did it happen?</i>

236
00:18:01,160 --> 00:18:04,176
<i>Mother! Mother.</i>

237
00:18:18,111 --> 00:18:20,070
<i>Second Uncle?</i>

238
00:18:50,711 --> 00:18:54,210
Report! Li Jiancheng and his sons are all dead.

239
00:18:55,560 --> 00:18:58,360
General Yuchi has gone to guard the emperor.

240
00:19:35,260 --> 00:19:37,390
Guards.

241
00:19:37,390 --> 00:19:38,387
Master.

242
00:19:38,387 --> 00:19:40,254
Ask someone and send it to East Palace.

243
00:19:40,254 --> 00:19:42,521
Be sure to invite Crown Prince to read it.

244
00:19:42,521 --> 00:19:43,510
Yes.

245
00:19:43,511 --> 00:19:44,449
Hurry!

246
00:19:44,449 --> 00:19:46,350
<i>It's too late.</i>

247
00:19:46,350 --> 00:19:47,821
Too late.

248
00:19:47,822 --> 00:19:51,054
Xuancheng, it's late.

249
00:19:51,054 --> 00:19:53,170
<i>[Fang Xuanling]</i>

250
00:19:54,844 --> 00:19:56,410
You...

251
00:19:56,410 --> 00:20:00,000
<i>[Crown Prince, Xuancheng]</i>

252
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:01,660
Leave here.

253
00:20:03,522 --> 00:20:05,560
Xuancheng,

254
00:20:05,560 --> 00:20:08,321
you've persuaded him a lot.

255
00:20:08,321 --> 00:20:10,632
Is it useful to write it?

256
00:20:10,632 --> 00:20:11,910
Why do you come here?

257
00:20:11,911 --> 00:20:13,670
I'm here to save you.

258
00:20:13,670 --> 00:20:15,054
I don't need it.

259
00:20:15,054 --> 00:20:20,421
But why are you going to suggest him again?

260
00:20:20,421 --> 00:20:23,587
The officials should be loyal to their masters.

261
00:20:23,587 --> 00:20:26,487
I should fulfill my duty.

262
00:20:26,488 --> 00:20:28,443
Let me tell you that

263
00:20:28,444 --> 00:20:30,643
a loyal official cannot die with his master.

264
00:20:30,644 --> 00:20:33,519
You've done your duty.

265
00:20:33,520 --> 00:20:35,160
All your duty.

266
00:20:36,911 --> 00:20:38,340
You!

267
00:20:38,340 --> 00:20:42,220
I'm here to prevent you.

268
00:20:42,222 --> 00:20:44,065
As I'm here,

269
00:20:44,066 --> 00:20:47,454
others will think you're under house arrest,

270
00:20:47,454 --> 00:20:50,078
so I can preserve both your reputation

271
