379
00:27:26,430 --> 00:27:28,750
Princess Yongning escaped while being chased.

380
00:27:28,750 --> 00:27:30,940
She's now missing.

381
00:27:31,699 --> 00:27:33,590
How come...

382
00:27:33,590 --> 00:27:36,370
She told me to wait for her here when she returns.

383
00:27:36,370 --> 00:27:39,940
